  "text": "The serum MIC-1 concentrations (pg/ml) were determined using a sensitive in-house sandwich enzyme-linked immunosorbent assay (ELISA), as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . All the samples were assayed at least two times, and the coefficient of variation between the samples was ,10%. ",
